OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,FHundreds of fathers are protesting
OL,7,Facross the UK to demand better
OL,8,Fpaternity pay.
OL,10,FThe Push for Paternity Leave marches
OL,11,Fbegan in London, Nottingham,
OL,12,FManchester and Leeds around midday
OL,13,FSaturday, with fathers seen pushing
OL,14,Fprams through city centres.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
