OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,FThose marching are calling for six
OL,7,Fweeks of paternity leave paid at 90%
OL,8,Fof salary for working fathers and
OL,9,Fkinship carers, and 12 weeks of
OL,10,Fmaternity pay at 90% of salary for all
OL,11,Fworking mothers.
OL,13,FThey are also calling for a
OL,14,Frequirement for employers to publish
OL,15,Ftheir parental leave policies.
OL,17,FAt present, new dads can only take up
OL,18,Fto two weeks' paid leave in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
