OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,F"It causes lots of problems for dads,"
OL,7,FErrol Murray, founder of parenting
OL,8,Forganisation Leeds Dads, told ITV News.
OL,10,F"If there's a traumatic birth, the dad
OL,11,Fmight not be able to be available to
OL,12,Fsupport the mum, the mum might feel
OL,13,Flost, alone, unsupported.
OL,15,F"It creates rifts between parents
OL,16,Fbefore the baby is even a month old.
OL,17,FSo it's really important that families
OL,18,Fget the best start in having a family
OL,19,Flife."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
