FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,FProtesters in London could be seen
OL,7,Fcarrying signs that said "equality
OL,8,Fstarts at home", "dads are caregivers
OL,9,Ftoo", and "fund fatherhood".
OL,11,FThey chanted "we believe, equal leave"
OL,12,Fand "six weeks pay, no delay" while
OL,13,Fstopping for photos in Trafalgar
OL,14,FSquare.
OL,16,F"I thought I was a really great hands
OL,17,Fon, involved dad, but my wife
OL,18,Fdisagreed, and we used to have a lot
OL,19,Fof arguments," Alex Trippier, host of
OL,20,Fpodcast Be a Happier Parent, told ITV
OL,21,FNews at the protest in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
