SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,F"I started reading books about
OL,7,Fmotherhood and it really made me
OL,8,Fappreciate how different the
OL,9,Fexpectations are that we put on mums,
OL,10,Fto the ones we put on dads.
OL,12,F"That really starts early with this
OL,13,Fkind of messaging about what is a mums
OL,14,Fjob - which is essentially everything
OL,15,F- and what is a dad's job, which is to
OL,16,Fgo to work and make more money, which
OL,17,Fthen mum's have to go and do too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,F"We have this complete structural
OL,7,Fimbalance and it is killing
OL,8,Frelationships and causing massive
OL,9,Fsuffering for couples. It's this
OL,10,Fperiod where you should be on the same
OL,11,Fteam, and people just aren't."
OL,13,FRecent research by Parenting Out Loud
OL,14,Fand YouGov found that fathers are more
OL,15,Fthan twice as likely as mothers to say
OL,16,Fthey share parenting equally, with 49%
OL,17,Fof dads describing their household as
OL,18,Fequal, compared with 21% of mums.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
