OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,FThe survey of 2,000 parents highlights
OL,7,Fa significant imbalance in childcare,
OL,8,Fwith mothers taking on most
OL,9,Fresponsibilities.
OL,11,FIt found 53% of mothers said their
OL,12,Fcareers had been negatively affected
OL,13,Fafter having children, compared with
OL,14,F13% of fathers, with nearly one in
OL,15,Feight mothers leaving paid work
OL,16,Faltogether.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
