OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777827949
OL,3,C'Fund fatherhood': Hundreds of dads
OL,4,Cmarch for paternity pay across UK
OL,6,FFrom April this year, new laws came
OL,7,Finto effect that granted unpaid
OL,8,Fparental leave from the first day in a
OL,9,Fnew job, which the government says
OL,10,Fwill give an additional 1.5 million
OL,11,Fparents increased flexibility to share
OL,12,Fchildcare responsibilities.
OL,14,FLast year, the chair of the Women and
OL,15,FEqualities Committee said the UK has
OL,16,Fone of the "worst statutory leave
OL,17,Foffers for fathers and other parents
OL,18,Fin the developed world".
